# cf-dns

Simple TUI to edit DNS records for cloudflare managed domains 

## Installation

Using pip:

```bash
pip install cf-dns-edit
```

Using uv:

```bash
uv tool install cf-dns-edit
```

## Usage

After installing, simply run

```bash
cf-dns-edit
```
